-%C3%81c-Thuy%C3%AAn/poem-wDrUerorKMQ5vQac70rIlQ">Thuỷ điệu ca đầu - Hoàng Châu Khoái Tai đình tặng Trương Ác Thuyên - 水調歌頭－黃州快哉亭贈張偓佺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/Thu%E1%BB%B5-ph%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-li%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%ADu/poem-BMyLzVyQTFbhXzxmlYYThQ">Thuỵ phường liên tửu - 瑞坊蓮酒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-GrfZ83486gEgzshT4ctASA">Đoàn Nguyễn Tuấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Tr%E1%BA%AFc-h%E1%BB%99-3/poem-uJibKfdkJlsaMkOOh5-yeQ">Trắc hộ 3 - 陟岵 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B9ng-Linh/T%E1%BB%B1-ch%C3%AD/poem-i37FTQ6NdbZ2K8DoCogQUA">Tự chí - 自誌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B9ng-Linh/author-jAIc3yh2UuGv391ocDI_pA">Bồ Tùng Linh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
